### PUT
### Modificar un producto
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{idToUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Kayak Explorer Pro",
    "price": 1300,
    "description": "Kayak recreativo mejorado para 2 personas"
}

### DELETE
### Borrar un producto
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{idToDelete}}

### IDs
